<br>
The Queen's mask was passed over to Teygra last night and now it was time fr the tribe to officially recognize Teygra as their new Queen.<br>
<br>
Ardyn wore her ceremonial amazon leathers, which consisted of: a navy blue leather battle skirt that slit up both sides revealing her thighs, a matching bra-like halter top that was outlined with golden intracate Ancient Amazon symbols, a braid of brown leather wrapped around her forehead with a golden center piece that dangled just above her nose.<br>
<br>
Her top was decored and fringed in white owl feathers, She was ready to step down and take control of her own Clan in Eire.<br>
<br>
A slender yet built arm raised as silence blanketed the crowd. The arm went around her back and was clasped by the opposite hand. <br>
<br>
&quot;A Queen's reign rises and falls like the sun. As the sun set last night, so has my time here as your Queen. I feel honoured that I could command you and protect you, and I feel forever changed because you have taught me many things that can not be taught in schools. But As the sun rises, it rises with a New Queen, my Aunt, Teygra O'the Wind.&quot;<br>
<br>
The Amazons salute Ardyn-Tyger and she gracefull and proudly returns the salute. She hands over the mask of the Queen to her Aunt with a smile.<br>
<br>
&quot;I know you shall serve them well, dear Aunt.&quot;<br>
<br>
Ardyn turned back to the cheering crowd, and stepped down the ivory stairs, she stood infront of the crowd looking up at her Aunt, smiling ever so proud.<br>
<br>
&quot;Speech!&quot;, the crowd demanded from the new Queen.  <p>¤Ardyn-Tyger O'the Wind¤<br>
