<br>
&quot;Amazons, raise your weapons, and arms to the new Queen! Honour her as you would any other Queen!&quot;<br>
<br>
The tribe on command and unseaths their weapons, rases them skyward.<br>
<br>
&quot;Hail Queen Teygra!&quot;<br>
<br>
And as Ardyn started chanting this, the tribe followed all in sync with each other, praising their new leader.<br>
